These two people got into the car without being stopped.

289
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:43,399
You're so slow

290
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:45,360
that you can't even catch two injured boys.

291
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:47,320
If they were like that just now, they would fight.

292
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,360
Don't talk too loud.

293
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,840
Don't disturb your aunt.

294
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,960
She's too tired.

295
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,840
I'm so worried about her.

296
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,240
Who wouldn't worry about her?

297
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:56,759
Wait, wait, wait.

298
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,399
Wait a minute.

299
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,679
What's the situation now?

300
00:11:59,039 --> 00:11:59,600
Now...

301
00:12:01,039 --> 00:12:01,480
Bro,

302
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:02,320
I'll

303
00:12:02,399 --> 00:12:03,360
go back to the clinic

304
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,720
and make some mung bean porridge.

305
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,279
It's hot,

306
00:12:05,759 --> 00:12:06,399
and it'll help cool down.

307
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,440
Alright.

308
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:09,000
Then I'll go buy some

309
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:10,679
pies and other things she likes to eat.

310
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:13,200
Recovery requires energy.

311
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,080
Thank you.

312
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,559
It's my pleasure.

313
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,879
As for your injuries,

314
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,279
don't mention it to anyone.

315
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:24,879
Let's go.

316
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:41,360
The part of the aircraft wing is a bit loose.

317
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,480
Here you are.

318
00:13:03,759 --> 00:13:04,879
Some parts

319
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,519
can't hold on anymore

320
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:08,919
and need to be replaced.

321
00:13:09,399 --> 00:13:11,960
But this old model is hard to find.

322
00:13:12,559 --> 00:13:13,480
I don't understand your stuff.

323
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,759
Is it hard to find?

324
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:15,639
It's hard to say.

325
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:17,200
I'll ask around.

326
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:18,879
How about this?

327
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,320
You go ahead.

328
00:13:20,879 --> 00:13:21,399
Later,

329
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:23,080
I'll send a message

330
00:13:24,039 --> 00:13:24,799
to

331
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:26,480
the second-hand platform.

332
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,559
Maybe I can find it.

333
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:28,639
Okay.

334
00:13:28,799 --> 00:13:29,360
Okay.

335
00:13:36,679 --> 00:13:37,440
Auntie,

336
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:39,759
what spell did you cast on them?

337
00:13:39,879 --> 00:13:41,000
They're getting along so well.

338
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:44,799
I'm not comfortable with it.
